    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《UNO™》将经典卡牌游戏升级为充满活力的个性化体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照颜色、数字或符号匹配卡牌，打出行动卡让游戏更加刺激，与其他玩家一较高下，看看谁能先清空自己的手牌。打出最后一张卡的时候，别忘了喊出“UNO!”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这还是你熟悉的《UNO》，现已加入全新玩法连接彼此。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >按你的方式游玩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/470220/extras/32d72801f52788bff836b07d4dcb3cf0.poster.avif?t=1765229632\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/470220/extras/32d72801f52788bff836b07d4dcb3cf0.webm?t=1765229632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/470220/extras/32d72801f52788bff836b07d4dcb3cf0.mp4?t=1765229632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以线上联机，也可坐着沙发本地对战，既可组队 2v2 竞技，也能开启多人大混战。将“抢牌”、“叠加”、“7-0换牌”等当家规则组合使用，打造属于你的狂欢派对。想要体验更多花样？那就试试精彩的 DLC！每个扩展包都能为卡牌游戏注入全新的机制和独特的玩法！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集、自定义、再好好露一手</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/470220/extras/dd307cc7572a16cae1d3f184dba19b6d.poster.avif?t=1765229632\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/470220/extras/dd307cc7572a16cae1d3f184dba19b6d.webm?t=1765229632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/470220/extras/dd307cc7572a16cae1d3f184dba19b6d.mp4?t=1765229632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过“MyDesign”功能，你可以深度定制《UNO》游戏的每个细节。用金币解锁缤纷主题面板、特色卡组、个性音乐、专属头像等，一起打造属于你的游戏空间吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一起加入，体验线上乐趣</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/470220/extras/332ed1b75e0a3ec8856ca3c605580dcf.poster.avif?t=1765229632\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/470220/extras/332ed1b75e0a3ec8856ca3c605580dcf.webm?t=1765229632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/470220/extras/332ed1b75e0a3ec8856ca3c605580dcf.mp4?t=1765229632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每周“欢乐时光”期间，你都能免费试玩一个不同的 DLC。限时探索新鲜玩法、疯狂规则和主题卡组！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >千万别忘了加入 Twitch UNO 社区！主播会开启“聊天大混战”模式，让粉丝实时投票，做左右战局发展。Twitch 扩展程序现已上线，解锁更多互动姿势！</p>",
